{"type": "article", "id": 28726, "title": "食材包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-27T06:51:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121010AQvS9wylFIMouzaB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/38426641/BABEL-Cooks-Ingredients\">BABEL</a> 的食材系列包装是希腊设计学生 Makrina Oikonomidou 的毕业作品。为了强调食材丰富的来源地，Oikonomidou 设计了一套调色板，搭配了代表产地的标志性图案和文字说明。每一个包装盒所使用的纸由 Oikonomidou 手工制成，这个过程中还加入了对应的食材，包装上斑驳的颜色也是因此而来。为了让顾客更清楚地看到食材，盒子的左右两侧采用了镂空设计。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121008CuRePhi92sFXQ8xI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121009kuTs501EwH4iy7ng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121009bux7ieFSO5UmWpV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121010fDkKTr2RLFQCgiYn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}